WEBVTT

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:00.936
Bu kishi menga yoqib qoldi.

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:03.856
Endi men nima qilishni istashimni
bilaman, deb o’yladim.

00:02:03.880 --> 00:02:06.016
O’sha kecha oilamga shunday xat yozdim

00:02:06.040 --> 00:02:08.336
"25 yoshimgacha

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:10.976
dunyodagi eng katta kompaniyani quraman

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:12.936
va bu kompaniya Microsoftni
sotib oladi."

00:02:12.960 --> 00:02:14.856
(Kulgu)

00:02:14.880 --> 00:02:17.496
Men dunyoni zabt etish g’oyasiga
tamoman yopishib oldim.

00:02:17.520 --> 00:02:18.720
dominantlik, to’g’rimi?

00:02:19.160 --> 00:02:21.976
buni ichimdan to’qiganim yo’q, 
o’sha xatni yozgandim.

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:23.336
Mana o’sha xat.

00:02:23.360 --> 00:02:25.336
(Kulgu)

00:02:25.360 --> 00:02:27.176
Buni o’qib chiqishingiz shart emas

00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:28.976
(Kulgu)

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:32.240
Qolaversa, bu yomon husnixat,
lekin ba’zi muhim so’zlarni belgilab